prodNameC: 伊敏升糖素放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Glucagon Antiserum (GND1): Lyophilized glucagon antiserum, raised in rabbits, with preservative.
125I Glucagon (GND2): Lyophilized, iodinated synthetic human glucagon, with preservative.
Glucagon Zero Calibrator (GND3): Lyophilized zero calibrator in a protein-based matrix, with preservative.
Glucagon Calibrator F (GND8): Lyophilized calibrator containing synthetic human glucagon in a protein-based matrix, with preservative.
Precipitating Solution (GNRG): consisting of goat anti-rabbit gamma globulin (GARGG) and dilute polyethylene glycol (PEG) in saline, with gentamicin as a preservative.
Glucagon Controls (GNCO1, GNCO2): containing synthetic human glucagon in a protein-based matrix, with preservative.
